\s Pahali pa Salama tamu
\zon1 4
\zoli1 \bd Pahali pa \bd*\bd Salama \bd*\bd tamu ni mbele yake Bwana\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Makosa ni pahali pale kwa kututesa tena.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ee Yesu Mukombozi uliyetumwa kwetu, Uchunge watu wako wote karibu nawe.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Pahali pa furaha nzuri ni mbele yake Bwana\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Tunapoweza kukutana naye Mwokozi wetu.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ee Yesu Mukombozi uliyetumwa kwetu, Uchunge watu wako wote karibu nawe.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Pahali pa uhuru vile ni mbele yake Bwana\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Pahali pa furaha tele na ustarehe kweli.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ee Yesu Mukombozi uliyetumwa kwetu, Uchunge watu wako wote karibu nawe.\bdit*
